'''约翰·迈克尔·霍索恩'''（{{lang-en|John Michael Hawthorn}}，{{bd|1929年|4月10日|1959年|1月22日|catIdx=Hawthorn}}）是一位英国赛车手，出生于[[约克郡|约克郡]]的{{link-en|梅克斯伯勒|Mexborough}}。霍索恩在1950年开始赛车生涯，并在1958年成为了第一位在[[一级方程式|一级方程式]]中赢得[[F1世界车手冠军列表|车手世界冠军]]的英国人。<ref name=Skilleter>{{Cite book | author =Bailey Skilleter|title = Mike Hawthorn: Golden Boy| publisher =PJ Publishing Ltd.| date =2015| ISBN =978-1-908658-06-7|accessdate=2022-01-15| language =en}}</ref>受到队友[[彼得·柯林斯|彼得·柯林斯]]于{{le|1958年德国大奖赛|1958 German Grand Prix|德国大奖赛}}死亡的影响，他在夺冠后不久即宣布退役。在退役三个月之后，迈克·霍索恩死于一场道路交通事故。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mike Hawthorn's fatal accident|url=http://www.mike-hawthorn.org.uk/finality.php|access-date=2014-10-30|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219120038/http://www.mike-hawthorn.org.uk/finality.php|archive-date=2015-12-19}}</ref>

除了一级方程式之外，霍索恩在[[勒芒24小时耐力赛|勒芒24小时耐力赛]]中也取得了成功。他与英国赛车手{{le|艾弗·布博|Ivor Bueb}}搭档，赢得了{{le|1955年勒芒24小时耐力赛|1955 24 Hours of Le Mans}}的冠军，<ref name="teamdan.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.teamdan.com/archive/wsc/1955/55lemans.html |title=1955 Le Mans 24 Hrs |access-date=2015-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232029/http://www.teamdan.com/archive/wsc/1955/55lemans.html |archive-date=2016-03-03 |url-status=dead }}</ref>而这场賽事同時也發生了賽車史最严重的[[1955年勒芒惨剧|死傷事故]]，這場事故也與霍索恩有直接關係。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.conceptcarz.com/view/f1/teamsBySeason.aspx?driverTeamArticleID=160&driverID=65 |title=Mike Hawthorn & the 1955 24 Hours of Le Mans: The Cause and the Effect |publisher=ConceptCarz.com |access-date=2013-04-15 |archive-date=2022-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220115124731/http://www.conceptcarz.com/view/f1/teamsBySeason.aspx?driverTeamArticleID=160&driverID=65 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC Four">{{cite AV media|date= 2010-05-16|title= Deadliest Crash:the Le Mans 1955 Disaster|medium= 纪录片|language= en|url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/b00sfptx/b00sfptq/The_Deadliest_Crash_the_Le_Mans_1955_Disaster/|access-date= 2022-01-15|publisher= BBC Four documentary|archive-date= 2010-07-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100729004937/http://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/b00sfptx/b00sfptq/The_Deadliest_Crash_the_Le_Mans_1955_Disaster/|dead-url= no}}</ref>

